  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK682">
<l>aṉpaṟi vārāynta colvaṉmaitū turaippāṟ </l>
<l>kiṉṟi yamaiyāta mūṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Love (to his sovereign), knowledge (of his affairs), and a discriminating power of speech (before other sovereigns) are the three sine qua non qualifications of an ambassador.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
